description: I was walking through my neighborhood when I saw a young man leaving a small, dirty casino. He had such a friendly smile so I immediately tried to talk him into some money-games. Unfortunately he rejected. I was really persistent that day so I really managed that he at least showed me his tiny butt. I never visited a casino before but obviously young men like them. So I decided to have look inside. And indeed around the corner the next cutie was gambling. He played a game on a slot-machine which I didn´t really understand but it looked like he lost a lot. He looked very sad and it was just a question of the amount to talk him into a lot. So I was something like a helping angel this day. And a horny one.
title: Czech Hunter 60
